dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.systemtemplate

Interface ISystem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable

    public interface ISystem
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    ISystem: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    The top level element of the System Description. The System description defines five major elements: Topology, Software, Communication, Mapping and Mapping Constraints. The System element directly aggregates the elements describing the Software, Mapping and Mapping Constraints; it contains a reference to an ASAM FIBEX description specifying Communication and Topology.
